lead_paragraph: Nathalie Boy de la Tour was elected president of the French Professional League (LFP) on Friday after former national team  coach Raymond Domenech's candidacy was rejected by the general assembly.

headline.print_headline: Boy De La Tour First Woman Elected French League President
